# Terraform local files
.terraform/
**/.terraform/*
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
crash.log
crash.*.log
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json

# Terraform plan files
*.tfplan
plan.out

